# Remember to never publicly share your keystore.
# See https://flutter.dev/to/reference-keystore
key.properties
**/*.keystore
**/*.jks

# Exception: the committed release.keystore is intentionally tracked so
# every CI build signs APKs with the same key (otherwise GitHub Actions
# generates a fresh ephemeral debug key per run, breaking app updates
# with "package conflict"). The password is intentionally not secret —
# this keystore only proves "same source", not anything sensitive.
!app/release.keystore
